    <h3>‚ùå Payment Unsuccessful</h3>
    <p>We were unable to process your <strong>{{#if (eq paymentType 'deposit')}}Deposit Payment{{else}}Winner Payment{{/if}}</strong> for auction <strong>{{auctionCode}}</strong>.</p>
